data.description: SELLER ASSIST - 2/1 BUYDOWN - BUYER COULD OBTAIN INTEREST RATE UP TO TWO POINTS BELOW CURRENT MARKET VALUE-SAVING THEM UP TO $6,000 OVER THE FIRST TWO YEARS. Option to settle before the end of the year or in January after the Holiday rush is over. NOTHING TO DO BUT MOVE IN - to this beautiful home on a quiet dead-end lane.  From the minute you step onto the welcoming covered front porch & enter the front door you will feel at home in this lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath cape cod home.  Massive living room with lots of natural light coming through the picture window & French doors which lead out to the patio & above ground pool with new large deck.  Hardwood floors in dining room & bedrooms. The first floor features an updated kitchen/dining room, newly remodeled bathroom (July 2023) & two bedrooms.  Laundry room & pantry are conveniently located just off the kitchen.  Spacious Master Suite on the second floor includes a luxurious custom tile master bath with soaking tub, extra-large walk-in tiled shower with seat & double sinks. Walk-in closet completes the Master Suite.   Fully finished basement can be used as an additional bedroom or family room.  One car attached garage with roomy storage area.  Fun wooden playset in back yard remains with the home.  Less than 15 minutes from PA Turnpike Mahoning Valley exit & Lehigh Canal Park.  Only 7 minutes from the Lehighton Trailhead-D & L Tail Spur for hiking & biking!   Lovely, tranquil yard with a captivating view of the mountains.
